name: 1 Camou TPU Diaper
description:
Diaper Information:

-Elastic pocket opening at the back for easy stuffing.
-Hip snaps - prevent wing drooping.
-Cross over tab snap.
-3 rows of snap buttons in the center, that will transform the diaper from small to medium and to large.
-One size diaper and has multiple overlap snaps placement in the waist, yield a better fit.
-Fits to 8-36 lbs.
-It can also be use as a cover.

-Waterproof outer layer and is made of soft and durable TPU fabric. Thermoplastic polyurethane (TPU) is a composition specifically adapted to produce non-porous membranes exhibiting waterproof and water vapor transmissible.

-Inner layer is made of micro suede cloth.

You are buying: 1 diaper and 1 large microfiber inserts.
